{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Entity","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Entity","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> 实体是一段以连字号（<code>&amp;</code>）开头、以分号（<code>;</code>）结尾的文本（字符串）。实体常常用于显示保留字符（这些字符会被解析为 HTML 代码）和不可见的字符（如“不换行空格”）。你也可以用实体来代替其他难以用标准键盘键入的字符。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 很多字符都有易于记忆的实体。例如版权符号 (<code>©</code>) 的实体是 <code>&amp;copy;</code>。对于没那么容易记住的字符，例如 <code>&amp;#8212;</code> 或 <code>&amp;#x2014;</code>，你可以查看 <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/named-characters.html#named-character-references\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">参考表</a> 或使用 <a href=\"https://mothereff.in/html-entities\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">解码工具</a>。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"保留字符","title":"保留字符","isH3":false,"content":"<p>有一些特别的字符被保留用于 HTML 中，这意味着浏览器会将这些字符解析为 HTML 代码。例如，如果你使用小于号（<code>&lt;</code>），浏览器会将其后的文本解析为一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Tag\">tag</a>。</p>\n<p>为了将这些字符显示为文本，需要使用相应的字符实体来代替它们，如下表所示。</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>字符</th>\n      <th>实体</th>\n      <th>说明</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&amp;</td>\n      <td><code>&amp;amp;</code></td>\n      <td>解析为实体或字符引用的开头</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&lt;</td>\n      <td><code>&amp;lt;</code></td>\n      <td>解析为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Tag\">tag</a> 的开头</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>&gt;</td>\n      <td><code>&amp;gt;</code></td>\n      <td>解析为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Tag\">tag</a> 的结尾</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\"</td>\n      <td><code>&amp;quot;</code></td>\n      <td>解析为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Attribute\">attribute</a> 的值的开头和结尾</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/named-characters.html#named-character-references\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">字符实体的官方列表</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"保留字符","id":"保留字符"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"HTML 实体是一段以连字号（&）开头、以分号（;）结尾的文本（字符串）。实体常常用于显示保留字符（这些字符会被解析为 HTML 代码）和不可见的字符（如“不换行空格”）。你也可以用实体来代替其他难以用标准键盘键入的字符。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Entity","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Entidad","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Entité","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Entity (エンティティ)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Сущности","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/entity","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/entity/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Entity","title":"Entity"}],"pageTitle":"Entity - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}